<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-status bg-success"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Congratulations!👏</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
        <p><div class="text-muted">Congratulations! You’ve been accepted!</div></p>
        <div class="text-muted">The event is from October 12th-14th at the University of Massachusetts Amherst.  In order to participate, make sure to rsvp with the button below.</div>
        <p><div class="text-muted">By clicking the RSVP button you are letting us know that you will <b> definitely</b> come to the event. We will be reserving swag, food and more for you. So please only RSVP if you are 100% sure you’ll be attending.</div></p>
        <br>
        <center>
          <%= link_to 'RSVP For The Event', rsvp_path, class: 'btn btn-success' %>
        </center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-status bg-purple"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Traveling 🚌</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
        <h3>Free buses will be provided!</h3>
        <p>Round trip travel from Boston & New York will be provided. </p>
        <p>We will send the link to sign up for the buses on Wednesday October 3rd.</p>
        <p>You will need to RSVP to sign up for the bus.</p>
        <div style="width:100%;height:0;padding-bottom:56%;position:relative;"><iframe src="https://giphy.com/embed/xT9KVBpc46FKGuAUaQ" width="100%" height="100%" style="position:absolute" frameBorder="0" class="giphy-embed" allowFullScreen></iframe></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-4">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-status bg-blue"></div>
      <div class="card-header">
        <h3 class="card-title">Getting to the Hackathon 🚶‍</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
        <p><div class="text-muted">HackUMass happens at the Integrated Learning Center(ILC) at the University of Massachusetts Amherst.</div></p>
        <p><div class="text-muted">If you’re driving to the event, you must park in Lot 44, Lot 20, or Lot 22 and then walk over to our venue. Check out our venue on Google Maps if you have problems navigating campus.</div></p>
        <div class="text-muted">If you have any questions, ask us know at team@hackumass.com </div>
        <br>
        <center>
          <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/851VYrC6oLJ2" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary">See Our Venue on Google Maps</a>
        </center>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
